                            <comment id="18018146" author="maedhroz" created="Thu, 4 Sep 2025 15:40:09 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;It&apos;s possible to simply rebuild the index after the upgrade completes, but it should never happen in the first place. Note that SAI dos not have this problem, as it indexes SSTables, not entire tables via &lt;tt&gt;SIM#indexPartition()&lt;/tt&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
